<A NAME="topicVRToolClippingMode"></A>

<H2>Clipping Mode</H2>
This tool is used to clip the mesh.<P>

<H2>Usage</H2>

<OL>


<LI>
Select the item "Clipping Mode" in the VR menu.

<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<CENTER><img align="center" src="vrClippingMode0.png"></CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>


<LI>
Hold the trigger and move the controller to clip the mesh. <FONT COLOR="red" FACE="Arial, Lucida Sans">This only affects the mesh visualization, there will be no data loss.</FONT>

<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<CENTER><img align="center" src="vrClippingMode1.png">  &nbsp&nbsp&nbsp  <img align="center" src="vrClippingMode2.png"></CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>

</OL>

<H2>Shortcuts</H2>

<UL>
<LI> Trigger - Create the clipping plane.
</UL>


